Uttar Pradesh
Sep 09, 2014
Child Sexual Abuse, Rape
Description:
			A minor girl was allegedly raped by a neighbour while she was sleeping in the courtyard of her house at a village in Doghat police station area here, police said today.

The incident took place on Sunday night when the 15-year-old girl was sleeping in the courtyard while her family members were on the terrace.

A youth living in the neighbourhood barged into the house and raped her, police said.

As she raised the alarm, the youth fled.

The girl has been sent for medical examination, they added.


